log.title: SCHREI by Helios and Valentina - Neuroshack - NFT Music
log.desc: This was our first experimental track for the chronical series. Valintina gave a 'liquid' style intro. and intense vocals from Helios over experimental neurofunk sounds. This was Helios' first track with the NS crew.

log.title: The Swamp Chronicals Part 1
log.desc: This scfi/horror story was developed last year and was intended to be an animation for a film festival. Due to a small budget we only did one part of the story as an audiobook, hope you enjoy it.
